    <div class="container">
      <div class="web-section">
        <div class="web-section-title" data-i18n="howTo">How To Use</div>
        <div class="my-5">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 details">
              <h2 data-i18n="steps">Steps</h2>
              <ol type="i">
                <li data-i18n="step1">
                  Locate the 'Complaint title' section at the top and provide a title for your complaints.<br/>
                  <div data-i18n="example1">

                    Examples: 'Road and Transportation,' 'Health and Hospital,' or 'Education.'
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li data-i18n="step2">
                  Descriptions section: Provide details like the exact location, duration of the problem, affected area, number of people affected, and other relevant information.<br/>
                  <div data-i18n="example2">

                    Example: Shortage of clean drinking water in 'Handigau' near the Yellow Bridge (Kathmandu Municipality ward No. 3). Pipes provided by Kathmandu Municipality have been broken for three weeks, affecting at least 10,000 people. Urgent pipe repairs are needed.<br/>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li data-i18n="step3">
                  Complaints Category: If you want your complaints visible to everyone then choose 'Public' or 'Private' for only yourself. <br/>
                </li>
                <li data-i18n="step4">
                  Area: Select the specific issue related to your complaint. You can choose options provided or 'other' for specific categories. <br/>
                </li>
                <li data-i18n="step5">
                  Upload Image: Upload photos of the affected area or damage caused by incidents. You can capture new photos or choose from your gallery, uploading multiple at once. <br/>
                </li>
                <li data-i18n="step6">
                  Click 'Submit' to register your complaint.
                </li>
              </ol>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6" style="height: 600px;">
              <img
              class="mblPic"
              src="../image/howToMobile.jpeg"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="my-5">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6 detail-image">
                <img
                src="../image/webHowTo.png"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 details-right">
                <h2 data-i18n="note">Note: </h2>
                <ol type="i">
                  <li data-i18n="note1">
                    You can register multiple complaints about different issues using the same process.<br/>
                  </li>
                  <li data-i18n="note2">
                    Explore the 'Total' section to view the number of other public complaints registered by users.<br/>
                  </li>
                  <li data-i18n="note3">
                    After submission, your complaints move to a queue. The progress section is manual, and the team will review and accept your complaints as soon as possible, completing your registration.<br/>
                  </li>
                </ol>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
